{"tid":761891,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當我想起你","createTime":"2018-07-30T19:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T20:30:43.000Z","uid":158103,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94442496741c799a7395f3064081ddcb885fe735","tid":761891,"uid":158103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T19:06:25.000Z","msg":"再記起一些古老的心事<br />\n再記起心中一串開心日子<br />\n曾在那似已遠遠的以前<br />\n共你差不多天天都相見<br />\n曾話過那天起 你已屬我 永不變<br />\n過去的經已不會再出現<br />\n遠去的一切只會更加遙遠<br />\n明白到各有各的去路 但我心中始終感到<br />\n能共你愛過 暖暖的令我自豪<br />\n<br />\n曾在我心 如此深深愛戀中 遺下憶記在腦中<br />\n從當天起 永都不可忘記<br />\n當我想～ 想起你 仍像昨天一般深愛你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2840583e126f3e5a3e2463031f9ea860e162f8a","tid":761891,"uid":157700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T19:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571282fbd13fdf047d044d949834dd5593e901dd","tid":761891,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T19:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf614ed790d2176101b7eb2bd516f1c9cc8a8b2","tid":761891,"uid":11329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T20:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907ff16de697cdba30a5951cd0d080c076a7c089","tid":761891,"uid":49091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T20:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}